4
00:00:13,931 --> 00:00:14,892
So I wanted to start out,

5
00:00:14,912 --> 00:00:17,352
think about what does it mean to design

6
00:00:17,392 --> 00:00:19,332
great interactive fiction that people love

7
00:00:19,492 --> 00:00:20,753
and to do it on this device.

8
00:00:21,753 --> 00:00:24,193
It means putting together two very distinct worlds.

9
00:00:24,633 --> 00:00:27,874
One world is, I think, well represented by Hollywood,

