00:00:31,614 --> 00:00:35,495
The other world is mobile, which is both the largest games platform on earth right now,

12
00:00:36,036 --> 00:00:38,977
as well as maybe the largest platform overall that we have to work on.

13
00:00:39,537 --> 00:00:44,879
So today I really want to walk through what are the parts we on episode have taken from both of these worlds

14
00:00:45,339 --> 00:00:47,220
to put together hit interactive fiction.

15
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:50,643
So as a way of background on kind of me and episode,

16
00:00:50,663 --> 00:00:52,345
for those of you that might not have it,

