00:21:27,442 --> 00:21:29,023
the engagement with those choices.

524
00:21:30,891 --> 00:21:35,973
So, we stay in this process until we get to something great,

525
00:21:36,113 --> 00:21:37,593
then we push it out to worldwide launch.

