00:21:38,173 --> 00:21:40,334
And that moment of launch is the moment where you learn,

527
00:21:40,394 --> 00:21:42,315
did you actually have a hit on your hands or not?

528
00:21:42,395 --> 00:21:44,435
You don't really know for sure up front,

529
00:21:44,696 --> 00:21:45,656
but there's so much you can do

530
00:21:45,696 --> 00:21:47,496
to give yourself a better chance along the way.

