00:23:03,186 --> 00:23:04,647
From there, you want to establish

560
00:23:04,667 --> 00:23:06,028
the right internal review loops,

561
00:23:06,808 --> 00:23:09,370
because you want to feel good about what you put out,

562
00:23:09,990 --> 00:23:12,012
but then you want to pilot to gather data and feedback.

563
00:23:12,172 --> 00:23:13,553
And honestly, we've never felt like

564
00:23:13,593 --> 00:23:15,094
we put something out too soon to pilot.

565
00:23:15,154 --> 00:23:16,815
We've often felt like we waited too long,

566
00:23:16,855 --> 00:23:17,976
spent too much time internally,

567
00:23:18,696 --> 00:23:20,197
but I think the sooner you put it out, the better.

568
00:23:21,385 --> 00:23:23,127
And then you want to iterate.

569
00:23:23,608 --> 00:23:24,508
And in this iteration,

570
00:23:24,629 --> 00:23:26,370
don't be afraid to blow up your story.

571
00:23:26,390 --> 00:23:28,052
I think that's the biggest thing.

